      value: "Other notable players include Shinizoma from the planet Hinora, the
        first player who managed to record a victory with more than 50 points difference
        in the play-off\u2019s and Korkon, from the planet Kaaman who was the first
        ever winner of the championship as well as the second most successful player
        in history with 6 championships, each of them being consecutive, which is
        why many Kaamanians consider him the best of all time."
